{"tid":1512801,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"文宣真係要林下點做","createTime":"2019-08-28T04:48:46.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-28T05:11:35.000Z","uid":306664,"like":0,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"103b76cdd50e63e938cc6335a9d8fb52245bdd73","tid":1512801,"uid":306664,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-28T04:48:46.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n反送中遊行引暴力 36人被捕<br />\n（法新社香港26日電） 香港警方今天表示，他們不 得不動用水炮車驅離群眾，並開槍示警，說這場延燒多 個星期的示威活動愈趨暴力。 昨天荃葵青遊行爆發「反送中」運動以來最嚴重的 警民衝突。警方共拘捕36人，年紀最小的是一名12歲男 童。 昨天爆發反送中以來最嚴重的警民衝突，警方頻遭 汽油彈攻擊與示威者近身襲擊，不但首度出動水炮車驅 離群眾，有警察在示威群眾步步進逼下跌倒，6警拔槍 ，更有一警對空開槍示警。 這是反送中遊行爆發以來，警察首次實彈射擊。<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.news.yahoo.com/%E5%8F%8D%E9%80%81%E4%B8%AD%E9%81%8A%E8%A1%8C%E5%BC%95%E6%9A%B4%E5%8A%9B-36%E4%BA%BA%E8%A2%AB%E6%8D%95-070502912.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.yahoo.com%2F%25E5%258F%258D%25E9%2580%2581%25E4%25B8%25AD%25E9%2581%258A%25E8%25A1%258C%25E5%25BC%2595%25E6%259A%25B4%25E5%258A%259B-36%25E4%25BA%25BA%25E8%25A2%25AB%25E6%258D%2595-070502912.html&d=zAhFImnUcMh%2FonyB55KWQwWTNdVklcLtcNqJxXVG150%3D&h=d1df15d7\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.yahoo.com/%E5%8F%8D%E9%80%81%E4%B8%AD%E9%81%8A%E8%A1%8C%E5%BC%95%E6%9A%B4%E5%8A%9B-36%E4%BA%BA%E8%A2%AB%E6%8D%95-070502912.html</a>"},{"pid":"0c982e23b6551ac7f0ee560f5b4c8dbd77369257","tid":1512801,"uid":284522,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-28T04:49:09.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/PWzcvgg.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FPWzcvgg.jpg&h=187c67d0&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n九月一號下午一點機場見<br />\n<br />\n901機場和你塞 Channel<br />\n<a href=\"http://t.me/stu